{"tid":1321920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[檢討］如何更有效傳達前線資訊","createTime":"2019-07-15T20:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T03:37:59.000Z","uid":148839,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"db678a094396c52366e302ca56d0a3d400078817","tid":1321920,"uid":148839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:16:31.000Z","msg":"其實發夢好多時候都已經上唔到網/load空氣，如果直接成個地區網絡收皮，手勢/資訊傳達就更有迫切性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現有問題：<br />\n1. 唔熟手勢意思/前線真正所需<br />\n（六角匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/長遮/索帶）<br />\n<br />\n2. 有難以以手勢表達嘅物資<br />\n（大膠袋/空樽）<br />\n<br />\n3. 未能有效停止過時資訊<br />\n- 對<span style=\"color: red;\">first aid/退後</span>等手勢/資訊過度敏感，令訊息極快向後傳遞<br />\n- ok手勢未能追趕訊息傳遞嘅速度<br />\n- 過份傳遞令<span style=\"color: red;\">非最前線first aider</span>冇意義地疲於奔命，令first aid分佈不平均<br />\n<br />\n4. 某前線物資充足的情況下無法傳達於身後傳送鏈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可行方法：<br />\n- 更新手勢資訊（文宣<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傳遞正確手勢知識</span></span><br />\n- 依靠遊走大聲公team<br />\n- 企高位兄弟諗清楚先做手勢<br />\nEg 無需做非緊急退後手勢（等人慢慢由前退後）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫推 同 諗下有冇其他問題/方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807b68cd620fea66747d05308532b8444d4687a8","tid":1321920,"uid":148839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71058b0c529e5aa715641ba1e901c41268784d60","tid":1321920,"uid":148839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T20:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2d5ebfa906a6f9011af60398d07624da8